<h4>Green roof updates</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Incentive increased: The green roof incentive has increased to $100 / m2.</li>
  <li>Structural Assessment Grants offered: Funding is now available to help determine whether an existing building can
    carry the additional load of a green roof.
  </li>
  <li>Not-for-profit corporations: All new construction projects by not-for-profit corporations are eligible for green
    roof incentives.
  </li>
</ul><h4>Cool roof updates</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Partial cool roof retrofits are now eligible. You can meet our 100% coverage requirement over time or all at
    once.
  </li>
  <li>New buildings eligible: Cool roof projects on new buildings with a gross floor area of less than 2000 m2 are now
    eligible.
  </li>
</ul><h4>Please note:</h4>
<ul>
  <li>You must submit your application before work on the roof starts.</li>
  <li>Green roof projects greater than $100,000 and cool roof projects greater than $50,000 may be eligible for funding
    in excess of the funding maximum, subject to Council approval.
  </li>
  <li>Incentives for eco-roof projects will be provided until funds are exhausted. We cannot guarantee funding for your
    eco-roof project will be available.
  </li>
  <li>Please note that all measurements are required in SQUARE METERS. Please use a <a
    href="https://www.google.ca/search?q=convert+10+square+feet+to+square+meters" target="_blank">conversion
    calculator<span class="sr-only">Opens in a new window</span><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-edit fa-external-link"></i></a> to convert square feet
    to square meters.
  </li>
  <li>Refer to our
    <a id="into_link_terms" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="CotApp.showModal({title:'Terms of Use Agreement', body: config.terms, originatingElement:$("#into_link_terms)});">
      Terms of Use Agreement
      <span class="sr-only">Opens in a modal dialog</span>
        <i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-edit fa-external-link"></i>
    </a>for further information.
  </li>
</ul>
